and with it's amazing display you just feel like you can do more.

00:03:08.875 --> 00:03:12.740
It's great for watching HD Videos in full Widescreen.

00:03:13.508 --> 00:03:17.900
and in Portrait Mode, iPhone 5 still fits so comfortably in your hand.

