Facebook is now integrated right into IOS 6

00:04:16.257 --> 00:04:20.510
So you can post Photos or share anything else 
 you want to directly from your apps.

00:04:21.862 --> 00:04:26.090
And now you can make a Facetime call right over the Cellular network.

00:04:26.612 --> 00:04:30.320
So no matter where you are, you're always 
 able to see the ones you love.

00:04:32.132 --> 00:04:34.610
Along with the experience of actually using it.

00:04:35.332 --> 00:04:37.630
What makes iPhone 5 so unique

00:04:38.512 --> 00:04:40.180
Is how it feels in your hand.

00:04:40.893 --> 00:04:42.650
The materials its been made with

00:04:43.054 --> 00:04:46.870
The remarkable precision with which its been built.

00:04:47.235 --> 00:04:54.250
Never before, have we built a product with 
 this extraordinary level of fit and finish.

00:04:55.069 --> 00:05:00.370
We've developed manufacturing processes that are our most complex and ambitious.

00:05:01.283 --> 00:05:06.090
Starting with the Aluminium, we've machined all of the surfaces of the enclosure.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:09.650
We then polish and texture them.

00:05:10.092 --> 00:05:17.330
We then use crystalline diamonds cut the chamfers it's so 
 exact that your left with a near mirror finish.

00:05:17.331 --> 00:05:22.710
These techniques created a dramatic distinction between the lightly textured back

00:05:22.711 --> 00:05:25.850
and its highly polished chamfered edge.

00:05:28.057 --> 00:05:33.870
This manufacturing precision extends of how these mini pieces seemingly come together.

00:05:34.978 --> 00:05:40.450
The in lay of the Product is matched 
 to housing of a highly sophisticated process.

00:05:42.044 --> 00:05:47.880
With the part of a Conveyor, 2 high 
 powered cameras take picture of the Housing.

00:05:48.629 --> 00:05:56.790
An Instantaneous analysis is done and then the best match 
 out of a possible 725 cuts is determined

00:05:57.749 --> 00:06:02.660
The variances from Product to Product, we now measure in microns. 

00:06:03.730 --> 00:06:05.620
We believe that we are going at such extreme lengths.

00:06:06.463 --> 00:06:11.440
Is the only way we can deliver this level of quality.

00:06:13.335 --> 00:06:18.780
To create the new iPhone, we began with a design we really love

00:06:19.846 --> 00:06:25.120
But to build it, implement it we had to look 
 way beyond what we knew to be possible.

00:06:26.129 --> 00:06:36.550
It took all of our learning, our best thinking to realize 
 something so simple, so clear and yet so truly extraordinary.

